      "id": "ch3",
      "number": "3",
      "title": "Standards",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "id": "b3_std",
          "label": "Standards",
          "defaultOn": true,
          "text": "BRL 4702/4708, KOMO certificate, NEN 6050, EN 13501-1, Bouwbesluit.\nWarranty: min {{warYr}} years (material + workmanship).\nAttach: KOMO cert, system data, warranty conditions, fire class.",
